Class FreeEdgeLabelLayoutModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.FreeEdgeLabelLayoutModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEdgeLabelLayoutModel

    public class FreeEdgeLabelLayoutModel
extends Object
implements IEdgeLabelLayoutModel
    FreeEdgeLabelLayoutModel allows placing edge labels at any location.

    • Method Detail

      • createModelParameter

        public Object createModelParameter(YOrientedRectangle labelBounds,
                                   IEdgeLayout edgeLayout,
                                   INodeLayout sourceLayout,
                                   INodeLayout targetLayout)
        Creates a model parameter that represents the given edge label position within this model.

        The created model parameter represents the current location of the given label.

        This parameter can be passed to getLabelPlacement(YDimension, IEdgeLayout, INodeLayout, INodeLayout, Object) to retrieve the current label box.

        Specified by:
        createModelParameter in interface IEdgeLabelLayoutModel
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if one or more of the given bounds' values are invalid, i.e., NaN
        Parameters:
        labelBounds - the oriented box of the label the parameter represents
        edgeLayout - the layout of the edge to which the label belongs
        sourceLayout - the layout of the source node of the label-owning edge
        targetLayout - the layout of the target node of the label-owning edge
        Returns:
        the model parameter representing the given label location
        See Also:
        getLabelPlacement(YDimension, IEdgeLayout, INodeLayout, INodeLayout, Object)

      • getDefaultParameter

        public Object getDefaultParameter()
        Gets the model parameter that encodes the default position of FreeEdgeLabelLayoutModel.

        The distance of the label to the edge's source point will be 20. The angle between the line to the center of the label and the first segment is 20 radians. The label is not rotated.

        This parameter can be passed to getLabelPlacement(YDimension, IEdgeLayout, INodeLayout, INodeLayout, Object) to retrieve the corresponding label box.

        Specified by:
        getDefaultParameter in interface IEdgeLabelLayoutModel
        Returns:
        the model parameter describing the default placement of the edge label
